{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Atlas RAG �?RAGAS 评估实验\n",
    "\n",
    "这个 Notebook 分成两个阶段：先调用项目�?RAG API 并保存原始回答，再使�?RAGAS 评分。修改指标或裁判模型时，可以从已保存的响应继续，避免重复调用业务 RAG�?
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 1. 初始化环"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from __future__ import annotations\n",
    "\n",
    "import json\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "from dataclasses import asdict\n",
    "from datetime import datetime\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "import httpx\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from dotenv import load_dotenv\n",
    "\n",
    "PROJECT_ROOT = Path.cwd().resolve()\n",
    "if not (PROJECT_ROOT / 'scripts' / 'ragas_evaluate.py').exists():\n",
    "    PROJECT_ROOT = PROJECT_ROOT.parent\n",
    "if not (PROJECT_ROOT / 'scripts' / 'ragas_evaluate.py').exists():\n",
    "    raise RuntimeError('请从项目根目录启�?JupyterLab，或把当前目录切换到项目根目录")\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, str(PROJECT_ROOT))\n",
    "load_dotenv(PROJECT_ROOT / '.env')\n",
    "\n",
    "from scripts.ragas_evaluate import (\n",
    "    collect_samples, load_cases, load_collected, login, run_ragas, summarize, write_jsonl,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'项目目录: {PROJECT_ROOT}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 2. 实验配置\n", "把示例数据集复制成自己的文件，并为每个问题填写人工标准答�?`reference`"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "DATASET_PATH = PROJECT_ROOT / 'eval' / 'ragas_dataset.example.jsonl'\n",
    "RESULT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / 'eval' / 'results'\n",
    "BASE_URL = os.getenv('RAG_EVAL_BASE_URL', 'http://localhost:8000')\n",
    "TOKEN = os.getenv('RAG_EVAL_TOKEN', '')\n",
    "USERNAME = os.getenv('RAG_EVAL_USERNAME', '')\n",
    "PASSWORD = os.getenv('RAG_EVAL_PASSWORD', '')\n",
    "LIMIT = None  # 调试时可设为 3\n",
    "REQUEST_TIMEOUT = 120.0\n",
    "METRICS = {'faithfulness', 'response_relevancy', 'context_precision', 'context_recall'}\n",
    "\n",
    "RESULT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n",
    "cases = load_cases(DATASET_PATH, LIMIT)\n",
    "pd.DataFrame([asdict(case) for case in cases])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 3A. 调用 RAG API 并保存原始响应\n", "执行前请启动 FastAPI。JWT 可直接配置，也可�?Notebook 使用用户名和密码登录"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "run_id = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')\n",
    "raw_path = RESULT_DIR / f'responses_{run_id}.jsonl'\n",
    "\n",
    "with httpx.Client(base_url=BASE_URL.rstrip('/'), timeout=REQUEST_TIMEOUT) as client:\n",
    "    access_token = TOKEN or login(client, USERNAME, PASSWORD)\n",
    "    samples = collect_samples(client, cases, access_token, retries=2)\n",
    "\n",
    "write_jsonl(raw_path, (asdict(sample) for sample in samples))\n",
    "print(f'已保�?{len(samples)} 条原始响�? {raw_path}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 3B. 可选：复用历史响应\n", "如果不想重新请求 RAG API，取消下面代码的注释并填入已�?JSONL"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# raw_path = RESULT_DIR / 'responses_20260622_120000.jsonl'\n",
    "# samples = load_collected(raw_path)\n",
    "# print(f'已载�?{len(samples)} 条历史响")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 使用 RAGAS 评分\n",
    "\n",
    "默认指标：\n",
    "- `faithfulness`：回答中的事实是否有检索上下文支持；\n",
    "- `response_relevancy`：回答是否切中问题（需�?Embedding 裁判服务）；\n",
    "- `context_precision`：靠前的检索片段是否真正相关；\n",
    "- `context_recall`：检索上下文是否覆盖标准答案需要的事实�?
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ragas_result = run_ragas(samples, METRICS)\n",
    "scores = ragas_result.to_pandas()\n",
    "summary = summarize(scores, samples)\n",
    "summary"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 5. 查看逐题结果"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "metadata = pd.DataFrame([asdict(sample) for sample in samples])\n",
    "metric_columns = [column for column in scores.columns if column not in metadata.columns]\n",
    "report = pd.concat([metadata.reset_index(drop=True), scores[metric_columns].reset_index(drop=True)], axis=1)\n",
    "display_columns = ['case_id', 'question', 'response', *metric_columns, 'latency_ms', 'degraded']\n",
    "report[display_columns]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 6. 指标可视化与薄弱样本"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "metric_means = report[metric_columns].mean(numeric_only=True).sort_values()\n",
    "ax = metric_means.plot.barh(figsize=(8, 4), xlim=(0, 1), title='RAGAS 指标均")\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('score')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "report['mean_score'] = report[metric_columns].mean(axis=1, numeric_only=True)\n",
    "report.sort_values('mean_score').head(10)[['case_id', 'question', 'mean_score', *metric_columns]]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 7. 导出报告"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "score_path = RESULT_DIR / f'ragas_scores_{run_id}.csv'\n",
    "summary_path = RESULT_DIR / f'summary_{run_id}.json'\n",
    "report.to_csv(score_path, index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n",
    "summary_path.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\n",
    "print(f'逐题报告: {score_path}')\n",
    "print(f'汇总报�? {summary_path}')"
   ]
  }
 ],
